Detailed Description

template<typename Tret, typename Tparam>
class meta::DbgFnWrap< Tret, Tparam >

Debugging IFnWrap.

A IFnWrap for debugging purposes, outputs the call details only.

Parameters:
Tret The method return type
Tparam The method parameter types (tuple)
